00:08:38.610 --> 00:08:46.049
So obviously then humility is also connected with having a mild temper and being meek.

00:08:46.610 --> 00:08:50.289
How so? Well, humility means we respect others.

00:08:51.169 --> 00:08:57.330
And of course included in that is our respective Jehovah, allowing him to do what he needs to do

