00:09:42.769 --> 00:09:50.370
Now interestingly, the Hebrew expression here humble yourself literally means stamp yourself down.

00:09:50.850 --> 00:09:57.009
So, do we see the lesson? When we're faced with a test like Moses was faced with,

00:09:57.009 --> 00:10:03.889
what should we do? Stamp ourselves down. Yes, hold off that hot temper.

00:10:03.889 --> 00:10:13.490
Yes, have full trust and hope in Jehovah and in that way we can be sure that he will view us as a meek person.
